<body>

    <header class="hero-meth">
        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <div class="hero-text-box-meth">
          <h1>Gift Shops</h1>
          <p>Discover the perfect place to find meaningful gifts for any celebration</p>
        </div>
      </header>      

  <section class="page-description">
    <p>
      Looking for the perfect gift to celebrate a special moment? Our curated selection of trusted gift shops offers everything from elegant flowers and luxury hampers to personalized keepsakes and tech gadgets. Whether you're planning a bridal celebration, a bachelor party, or simply want to surprise someone you love, these stores have you covered with quality, convenience, and unique gifting experiences. Browse through and find a shop that matches your occasion and style.
    </p>
  </section>
  

