      </div>
      
      <div class="shop-card">
        <img src="/img/images (1).png" alt="Lassana Flora Logo" class="shop-logo">
        <h3>Lassana Flora</h3>
        <p>Known for elegant flowers, gift boxes, wellness products and curated collections for weddings and events.</p>
        <a href="https://www.lassana.com/" target="_blank">Visit Shop</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="shop-card">
        <img src="/img/wasilogo_600x600.jpg" alt="Wasi.lk Logo" class="shop-logo">
        <h3>Wasi.lk</h3>
        <p>Wide variety of electronics and gift items with delivery service. Great for practical and modern gifts.</p>
        <a href="https://www.wasi.lk/" target="_blank">Visit Shop</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="shop-card">
        <img src="/img/images.png" alt="Labandi Logo" class="shop-logo">
        <h3>Labandi.com</h3>
        <p>Online gifting site with a selection of flowers, gift combos, chocolates, and celebratory essentials.</p>
        <a href="https://labandi.com/" target="_blank">Visit Shop</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="shop-card">
        <img src="/img/silver_aisle_logo.jpg" alt="Silver Aisle Logo" class="shop-logo">
        <h3>Silver Aisle</h3>
        <p>Luxury gifting platform offering curated gift boxes, flowers, and event-based gift items with delivery.</p>
        <a href="https://gift.silveraisle.com/" target="_blank">Visit Shop</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="shop-card">
        <img src="/img/Who-We-Are-Logo.png" alt="Who We Are LK Logo" class="shop-logo">
        <h3>Who We Are</h3>
        <p>Specializing in locally crafted, eco-friendly, and ethical gifts that are perfect for meaningful occasions.</p>
        <a href="https://whoweare.lk/gift-shop/" target="_blank">Visit Shop</a>
